79
00:03:11,760 --> 00:03:12,630
What's going on?

80
00:03:12,680 --> 00:03:14,890
Rainbow Dash
thinks Fluttershy's a tree.

81
00:03:14,930 --> 00:03:17,180
I do not think she's a tree.
I was just --

82
00:03:17,180 --> 00:03:19,180
Did you say
she was a tree?
No!

83
00:03:19,180 --> 00:03:20,930
Well, yes,
but not exactly.

84
00:03:20,980 --> 00:03:22,980
You know she's not a tree,
right?

85
00:03:22,980 --> 00:03:25,060
She's not a tree,
Dashie.

86
00:03:25,110 --> 00:03:26,570
I'd like to be a tree.

87
00:03:26,610 --> 00:03:29,190
Oh, for Pete's sake!

88
