[ Footsteps depart quickly ]

90
00:03:31,860 --> 00:03:33,530
[ Door creaks, slams ]

91
00:03:33,530 --> 00:03:35,490
Well,
that was kind of huffy.

92
00:03:35,530 --> 00:03:37,700
Huffy the magic dragon.

93
00:03:37,740 --> 00:03:38,870
[ Both giggle ]

94
00:03:38,910 --> 00:03:40,910
[ All giggling ]

95
00:03:40,950 --> 00:03:43,870
Would you all
