[ Sighs ]

104
00:03:59,600 --> 00:04:01,810
[ Birds chirping ]

105
00:04:01,850 --> 00:04:04,190
[ Hoofbeats rumble,
tracks clacking ]

106
00:04:06,190 --> 00:04:07,610
[ All snoring,
rumbling continues ]

107
00:04:07,650 --> 00:04:08,730
[ Thud! ]

108
00:04:08,770 --> 00:04:10,730
Huh?
Who gets what now?
Huh?

109
00:04:10,780 --> 00:04:12,150
[ Sloop! Sloop! Sloop! ]

110
00:04:12,190 --> 00:04:13,490
[ All gasp ]

111
00:04:13,530 --> 00:04:15,490
A buffalo stampede!

112
00:04:15,530 --> 00:04:16,570
Oh, wow!

113
00:04:16,620 --> 00:04:18,580
So noble,
all of them together.

114
00:04:18,580 --> 00:04:20,990
Rarity: I just love
their accessories.

115
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:24,210
They're getting awfully close
to the train.

116
00:04:30,210 --> 00:04:31,920
Aah!
Aah!Aah!
Aah!

117
00:04:31,920 --> 00:04:34,550
[ All shouting indistinctly ]

118
00:04:36,590 --> 00:04:38,640
[ Snoring ]

119
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:40,640
[ Creak! ]

120
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:43,060
[ Squeak! ]

121
00:04:46,940 --> 00:04:48,810
[ Tweet! ]

122
00:04:50,690 --> 00:04:54,070
Ooh! Looky!
Now they're doing tricks!

123
00:05:01,280 --> 00:05:03,200
Ooh! Ooh! Ooh!
Now do a back flip!

124
00:05:05,210 --> 00:05:07,620
[ Thud! ]
Or just jump?

125
00:05:08,250 --> 00:05:09,960
Hmm.

126
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:12,920
Something tells me
this isn't a circus act.

127
00:05:14,090 --> 00:05:15,670
Hey, there!
[ Gasps ]

128
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:16,800
Where you headed
in such a hurry?

129
00:05:18,260 --> 00:05:19,760
[ Grunts ]

130
00:05:21,760 --> 00:05:23,180
Wow.

131
00:05:23,220 --> 00:05:25,680
You're pretty quick
for someone so...bulky.

132
00:05:25,730 --> 00:05:27,560
No offense.

133
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:28,690
Huh?

134
00:05:30,270 --> 00:05:31,480
I just want to know --

135
00:05:32,820 --> 00:05:34,190
Hey!

136
00:05:34,230 --> 00:05:35,990
I'm talking to you!

137
00:05:36,030 --> 00:05:37,610
[ Whirl! Whirl! Whirl! ]

138
00:05:39,740 --> 00:05:41,160
Whoa!

139
00:05:42,620 --> 00:05:43,830
[ Grunts ]

140
00:05:43,870 --> 00:05:46,250
[ Screech! ]
I've got you now, you --

141
00:05:46,290 --> 00:05:48,540
[ Thud! Twang! ]

142
